          <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
          <h1>Plain-language privacy information.</h1>
          <p>This page explains how Rose &amp; Paw Digital Designs may handle information submitted through this website. It is not legal advice.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-inner policy-content">
          <h2>Information you choose to send</h2>
          <p>If you call, email, use the inquiry form, or contact Rose &amp; Paw Digital Designs through Facebook, you may provide details such as your name, business name, email address, phone number, service interest, budget or package interest, and message.</p>
          <h2>Quote form submissions</h2>
          <p>The quote request form is processed through Web3Forms so the message can be delivered by email. Web3Forms may receive the details you enter into the form, including your contact information and project message.</p>
          <h2>How information may be used</h2>
          <p>Information may be used to respond to inquiries, prepare quotes, discuss website design or digital design services, schedule appointments, provide project support, and follow up about requested work.</p>
          <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
          <p>Google Analytics 4 is configured with Measurement ID {{ business.analyticsId }}. Analytics loads only after a visitor accepts analytics cookies. It is used to understand website usage and contact interactions such as page views, phone or email clicks, and quote request interest. Visitors can reopen Cookie settings in the footer to revise or withdraw their choice.</p>
          <h2>Advertising tracking</h2>
          <p>Advertising tracking is not currently active. Advertising storage, user data, and personalization consent remain denied whether analytics cookies are accepted or rejected.</p>
          <h2>Third-party services and external links</h2>
          <p>Third-party services include Web3Forms for form delivery, Cloudflare Turnstile for form spam protection, Google Analytics 4 after analytics consent, and external links such as Facebook, email, and phone links. External websites have their own privacy practices.</p>
          <h2>No selling of personal information</h2>
          <p>Rose &amp; Paw Digital Designs does not sell personal information.</p>
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:{{ business.email }}" data-track="email_click">{{ business.email }}</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
